<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>BelQuantia - Inteligencia Financiera</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --teal: #00C2A8;
      --teal-dark: #009e88;
      --navy: #0D1F3C;
      --navy-mid: #1a3256;
      --gray-100: #F7F8FA;
      --gray-200: #ECEEF2;
      --gray-400: #9CA3AF;
      --gray-600: #4B5563;
      --gray-800: #1F2937;
      --white: #FFFFFF;
      --font: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      --radius: 12px;
      --radius-sm: 8px;
      --shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
      --shadow-lg: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.11);
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: var(--font);
      color: var(--gray-800);
      background: var(--white);
      line-height: 1.65;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    /* ─── NAV ─── */
    nav {
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.96);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      padding: 0 2rem; height: 68px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .nav-logo { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--navy); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .nav-logo span { color: var(--teal); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.75rem; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a { text-decoration: none; color: var(--gray-600); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; transition: color 0.2s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--navy); }
    .nav-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.35rem; }
    .badge-beta { font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 700; background: var(--teal); color: white; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .btn-nav { background: var(--teal); color: white !important; padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem; border-radius: 999px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.85rem; transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s; }
    .btn-nav:hover { background: var(--teal-dark) !important; transform: translateY(-1px); }

    /* ─── SHARED ─── */
    section { padding: 96px 2rem; }
    .container { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-label { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--teal); margin-bottom: 1rem; display: block; }
    h2 { font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem); font-weight: 800; color: var(--navy); letter-spacing: -0.5px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

    .btn-primary { display: inline-block; background: var(--teal); color: white; padding: 0.85rem 2rem; border-radius: 999px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.95rem; text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.2s; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,194,168,0.3); }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--teal-dark); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(0,194,168,0.4); }
    .btn-secondary { display: inline-block; background: white; color: var(--navy); padding: 0.85rem 2rem; border-radius: 999px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; text-decoration: none; border: 1.5px solid var(--gray-200); transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.15s; }
    .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--teal); color: var(--teal); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .btn-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    /* ─── HERO ─── */
    #hero { padding: 120px 2rem 96px; background: linear-gradient(160deg, #f0fdfb 0%, #ffffff 60%); text-align: center; }
    #hero .container { max-width: 800px; }
    .hero-eyebrow { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; background: #e6faf7; border: 1px solid #b2ede6; border-radius: 999px; padding: 0.35rem 1rem; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--teal-dark); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .hero-eyebrow::before { content: ''; width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--teal); border-radius: 50%; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
    @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1);}50%{opacity:0.5;transform:scale(1.4);} }
    h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; color: var(--navy); letter-spacing: -1px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--teal); }
    .hero-sub { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--gray-600); max-width: 660px; margin: 0 auto 1.25rem; }
    .hero-aside { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gray-600); font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    .btn-group.centered { justify-content: center; }

    /* ─── PROBLEMA ─── */
    #problema { background: var(--white); }
    .problema-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
    .problema-card { background: var(--gray-100); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 2rem; border: 1px solid var(--gray-200); }
    .problema-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; }
    .problema-card h3 .icon { width: 32px; height: 32px; background: var(--teal); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .problema-card ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
    .problema-card li { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--gray-600); display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; }
    .problema-card li::before { content: '·'; color: var(--teal); font-size: 1.4rem; line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .mensaje-clave { margin-top: 2.5rem; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg,#e6faf7,#f0fdfb); border-left: 3px solid var(--teal); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--navy-mid); }

    /* ─── SOLUCIÓN ─── */
    #solucion { background: var(--gray-100); }
    #solucion .sub { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--gray-600); max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .pilares { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
    .pilar { background: white; border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 2rem; border: 1px solid var(--gray-200); box-shadow: var(--shadow); transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; }
    .pilar:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); }
    .pilar.destacado { border: 2px solid var(--teal); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .pilar.destacado::before { content: 'Diferenciador clave'; position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 4px 12px; border-bottom-left-radius: 8px; }
    .pilar-icon { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .pilar h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .pilar p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.6; }
    .frase-clave { text-align: center; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); max-width: 680px; margin: 2.5rem auto 0; }

    /* ─── ECOSISTEMA ─── */
    #ecosistema { background: var(--navy); color: white; }
    #ecosistema h2 { color: white; }
    #ecosistema .sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; max-width: 560px; }
    .eco-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
    .eco-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 2rem; transition: background 0.2s; }
    .eco-card:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
    .eco-card .eco-icon { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .eco-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: white; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .eco-card p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); line-height: 1.6; }
    .eco-tag { display: inline-block; margin-top: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--teal); background: rgba(0,194,168,0.12); padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 999px; }
    #ecosistema .section-label { color: var(--teal); }

    /* ─── KELIXA ─── */
    #kelixa { background: var(--white); }
    .kelixa-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
    #kelixa h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2.1rem); }
    #kelixa .sub { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gray-600); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.7; }
    .validacion-pill { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; background: #fff7ed; border: 1px solid #fed7aa; border-radius: 999px; padding: 0.4rem 1rem; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; color: #c2410c; margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
    .kelixa-visual { background: var(--gray-100); border: 1px solid var(--gray-200); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 2rem; }
    .table-compare { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .table-compare th { text-align: left; padding: 0.6rem 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.72rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: var(--gray-400); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gray-200); }
    .table-compare td { padding: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200); color: var(--gray-600); vertical-align: middle; }
    .table-compare tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .col-con { color: var(--teal-dark); font-weight: 600; }
    .col-label { font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); }
    .check { color: var(--teal); font-weight: 700; margin-right: 4px; }
    .cross { color: #EF4444; margin-right: 4px; }

    /* ─── CAPACITACIÓN ─── */
    #capacitacion { background: var(--gray-100); }
    #capacitacion h2 { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    #capacitacion .sub { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--gray-600); max-width: 580px; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .caps-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
    .cap-card { background: white; border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 2rem; border: 1px solid var(--gray-200); box-shadow: var(--shadow); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; }
    .cap-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); }
    .cap-icon { font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .cap-tag { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 999px; width: fit-content; }
    .cap-tag.live { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
    .cap-tag.soon { background: #fef9c3; color: #854d0e; }
    .cap-tag.free { background: #e0f2fe; color: #075985; }
    .cap-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); }
    .cap-card p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.6; flex: 1; }
    .cap-card .cap-cta { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--teal); text-decoration: none; margin-top: auto; }
    .cap-card .cap-cta:hover { color: var(--teal-dark); }
    .metodo-banner { margin-top: 3rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--navy-mid) 100%); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 2.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .metodo-banner h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; color: white; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .metodo-banner p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); max-width: 520px; }
    .metodo-letras { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .letra-badge { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 8px; background: rgba(0,194,168,0.2); border: 1px solid rgba(0,194,168,0.4); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--teal); }

    /* ─── PROMPTS ─── */
    #prompts { background: linear-gradient(160deg,#e6faf7 0%,#f0fdfb 100%); }
    #prompts h2 { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    #prompts .sub { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--gray-600); max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    .prompts-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    .prompt-item { background: white; border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center; box-shadow: var(--shadow); border: 1px solid var(--gray-200); }
    .prompt-item .pi-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .prompt-item h4 { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }
    .prompt-item p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--gray-600); }

    /* ─── HISTORIA / FOUNDER ─── */
    #historia { background: var(--white); }
    .historia-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; }
    .founder-card { background: var(--gray-100); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 2rem; border: 1px solid var(--gray-200); text-align: center; }
    .founder-avatar { width: 80px; height: 80px; border-radius: 50%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal), var(--navy)); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 2rem; margin: 0 auto 1rem; }
    .founder-name { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .founder-title { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .founder-badges { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .f-badge { background: white; border: 1px solid var(--gray-200); border-radius: 999px; padding: 0.35rem 0.9rem; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy-mid); }
    .f-badge span { color: var(--teal); margin-right: 4px; }
    .historia-content h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .historia-content .origen { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; background: #f0fdfb; border: 1px solid #b2ede6; border-radius: 999px; padding: 0.35rem 1rem; font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--teal-dark); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .historia-content p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1.1rem; }
    .historia-content p strong { color: var(--navy); }
    .historia-quote { margin: 1.5rem 0; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg,#e6faf7,#f0fdfb); border-left: 3px solid var(--teal); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); font-size: 0.95rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--navy-mid); font-weight: 500; }
    .timeline { display: flex; gap: 0; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
    .tl-item { flex: 1; text-align: center; position: relative; padding-top: 1rem; }
    .tl-item::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; background: var(--gray-200); }
    .tl-item:first-child::before { left: 50%; }
    .tl-item:last-child::before { right: 50%; }
    .tl-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--teal); margin: -5px auto 0.6rem; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .tl-year { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--teal); }
    .tl-label { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--gray-600); }

    /* ─── PARA QUIÉN ─── */
    #para-quien { background: var(--gray-100); }
    #para-quien h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .quien-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
    .quien-card { text-align: center; padding: 2.5rem 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius); background: white; border: 1px solid var(--gray-200); transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }
    .quien-card:hover { border-color: var(--teal); transform: translateY(-3px); }
    .quien-card .q-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .quien-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .quien-card p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--gray-600); }

    /* ─── CTA FINAL ─── */
    #cta-final { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--navy-mid) 100%); text-align: center; }
    #cta-final h2 { color: white; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 1rem; }
    #cta-final .sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 1rem; max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 2.5rem; }

    /* ─── FORMULARIO ─── */
    #formulario { background: white; border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 2.5rem; max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); }
    #formulario h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    #formulario .form-sub { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--gray-600); margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
    .form-group { margin-bottom: 1.1rem; }
    .form-group label { display: block; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }
    .form-group input, .form-group select { width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--gray-200); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); font-family: var(--font); font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--gray-800); background: var(--white); outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
    .form-group input:focus, .form-group select:focus { border-color: var(--teal); }
    .btn-form { width: 100%; background: var(--teal); color: white; border: none; padding: 0.9rem; border-radius: 999px; font-family: var(--font); font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
    .btn-form:hover { background: var(--teal-dark); transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .form-note { text-align: center; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--gray-400); margin-top: 1rem; }

    /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
    footer { background: var(--gray-100); border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-200); padding: 2.5rem 2rem; }
    .footer-inner { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; }
    .footer-logo { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--navy); }
    .footer-logo span { color: var(--teal); }
    .footer-tagline { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--gray-400); margin-top: 0.2rem; }
    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .footer-links a { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--gray-400); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--navy); }
    .footer-copy { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--gray-400); }

    /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      section { padding: 72px 1.25rem; }
      .problema-grid, .pilares, .eco-grid, .quien-grid, .caps-grid, .kelixa-inner, .historia-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
      .prompts-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
      .timeline { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
      .tl-item::before { display: none; }
      .metodo-banner { flex-direction: column; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ─── NAV ─── -->
  <nav>
    <a href="#" class="nav-logo">
  <img src="logo-belquantia.png" alt="BelQuantia" style="height:28px;">
</a>Bel<span>Quantia</span></a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#kelixa" class="nav-badge">Kelixa <span class="badge-beta">beta</span></a></li>
      <li><a href="#prompts">Biblioteca</a></li>
      <li><a href="#capacitacion">Capacitación</a></li>
      <li><a href="#formulario" class="btn-nav">Acceso anticipado</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <!-- ─── HERO ─── -->
  <section id="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">Plataforma en validación activa</div>
      <h1>Inteligencia financiera para entender tus números y tomar <em>mejores decisiones</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">BelQuantia integra herramientas, análisis y recursos con inteligencia artificial para ayudar a emprendedores, empresas y contadores a transformar datos en información clara, confiable y accionable.</p>
      <p class="hero-aside">"No se trata solo de llevar la contabilidad. Se trata de entender qué está pasando con tu negocio."</p>
      <div class="btn-group centered">
        <a href="#formulario" class="btn-primary">Quiero participar y recibir acceso →</a>
        <a href="#kelixa" class="btn-secondary">Acceso anticipado</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── PROBLEMA ─── -->
  <section id="problema">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">El problema</span>
      <h2>El problema no es solo la contabilidad.<br />Es no entender los números.</h2>
      <div class="problema-grid">
        <div class="problema-card">
          <h3><span class="icon">🚀</span> Para emprendedores</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>No saben con certeza si están ganando o perdiendo</li>
            <li>Carecen de claridad financiera para crecer con confianza</li>
            <li>Toman decisiones importantes sin datos concretos</li>
          </ul>
